        <item>
            <title>中国邮政史上首枚数码邮票，售价 $298～6 万连区块链合约地址</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/digitalstampchina/life-tech/crypto-blockchain/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=digitalstampchina</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/digitalstampchina/life-tech/crypto-blockchain/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 10:00:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[区块链]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码邮票]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217581</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中国邮政史上首枚数码邮票《甲辰年》，仪式早前在香港数码港举行，由中国邮政香港有限公司、金玖银玖（香港）金融科技有限公司、北京龙源传统文化交流促进中心、香港大学金融创新及发展研究中心联合发行。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217584" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/65a9861ee4b017d96e6e-694x504.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="504" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/65a9861ee4b017d96e6e-694x504.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/65a9861ee4b017d96e6e.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dc528384492f4c55a13d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dc528384492f4c55a13d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dc528384492f4c55a13d.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这款邮票为中国邮政首枚发行于 Polygon 公有区块链的数码加密邮票。邮票图案印有龙年的龙样貌。发售价格入场费最低由港币 298 起。</p><p>邮票另有足金套装，黄金实物上印刻《甲辰年》数字邮票唯一区块链合约地址。数码邮票为集邮爱好者提供个人化服务，在区块链上铭刻个人化资讯，如签署收藏者的姓名、生日或赠送寄语等。</p><p>《甲辰年》生肖邮票小全张售价 298 港币</p><p>贺岁邮票金（0.1g 足金）售价 598 港币</p><p>纳福邮票金（9g 足金）售价 5998 港币</p><p>如意邮票金（49g 足金）售价 29998 港币</p><p>祥瑞邮票金（99g 足金）售价 59998 港币</p><p>资料来源：IT 之家</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/20/sfc-said-2-company-involve-in-crypto-scam/life-tech/crypto-blockchain/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">证监会：2 间公司涉加密货币诈骗，今日列入警示名单</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/digitalstampchina/life-tech/crypto-blockchain/">中国邮政史上首枚数码邮票，售价 $298～6 万连区块链合约地址</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
