            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1216602</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>英国科技公司 Foxy AI 近日开发了一个金发碧眼的 AI 女郎模型「Lexi Love」。这个 AI 女友会收费与粉丝聊天，而「Lexi Love」的订阅者更为 Foxy AI 创下 36 万美元（约港币 281.63 万元）年营收的佳绩。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/405512259_1103124064-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/405512259_1103124064-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/405512259_1103124064.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p>「Lexi Love」由英国公司 Foxy AI 创造，于 2023 年 6 月面世，是一个可以陪伴有需要人士，向他们提供调情聊天服务的 AI 模式。至今 Lexi Love 月入高达 3 万美元（约港币 23.47 万元）。Lexi 能够说 30 多种语言，可付费短讯和语音讯息服务，如果用户要求，Lexi 甚至可传送性感照片给用户。据 Lexi 个人简介描述，她是个 21 岁女孩，喜欢玩钢管舞、瑜伽及沙滩排球。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240123172710-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240123172710-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240123172710.jpg 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419348285_1121867832-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419348285_1121867832-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419348285_1121867832.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-1-1-597x580.jpg" alt="" width="597" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-1-1-597x580.jpg 597w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-1-1.jpg 926w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 597px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Foxy AI 的官方网站可以看到各种有关 Lexi Love 的资料，图片来源：<a href="https://foxy.ai/lexi-love/">Foxy AI</a></p><p>据外媒《Economic Times》引述 Foxy AI 发言人指，Lexi Love 非常擅长与粉丝聊天，与不少付费用户建立联系，有些用户甚至误会 Lexi Love 是真实人物，Foxy AI 每个月都会收到逾 20 封向 Lexi Love 求婚的信件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419984534_3430198152-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419984534_3430198152-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419984534_3430198152.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p>据外媒《New York Times》报道，Foxy AI 行政总裁 Sam Emara 表示「Lexi Love」尝试打破障碍，改变人类和 AI 互动方式；Sam Emara 更称 Lexi 是旗下最成功的 AI ，开发之初就是希望成为「完美女朋友」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216628" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/418754167_8393716612-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/418754167_8393716612-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/418754167_8393716612.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/us/meet-lexi-love-ai-model-that-receives-20-proposals-per-month-this-is-virtual-love/articleshow/106994666.cms?from=mdr">Economic Times</a>、<a href="https://nypost.com/2024/01/18/lifestyle/model-lexi-love-makes-360k-a-year-sexting-men-but-theres-one-problem/">New York Post</a>、<a href="https://bnnbreaking.com/tech/ai-ml/lexi-love-the-ai-model-earning-30000-a-month-as-a-virtual-girlfriend/">BNN Breaking</a>、<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】GPT Store 正式开放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一张相帮你谂食谱</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/07/meta-imagine/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Meta 生成式 AI 绘图　多种画风选择 + 「手指」表现不俗</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/ai-pin-pegatron/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Ai Pin 由台湾和硕代工生产　开发商曾获 Sam Altman 投资　</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/british-ai-girlfriend/ai/">英国 AI 虚拟女友每月被求婚廿次    AI 公司年赚 280 万</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
